{"tid":41754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"●[港版索姆河戰役] 莫失莫忘 紀念香港保衛戰Part 1","createTime":"2016-12-16T06:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T07:31:21.000Z","uid":53284,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37d9468b668a381bbd3e2d7fc1aa82b84a8a37ae","tid":41754,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:40:19.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=BHVGhwENv8XoGng4fVoh0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=45afa0ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 聖誕節，本應是喜氣洋洋，和平，又真是理所當然？可有想過，75年前的香港人，度過了截然不同的黑色聖誕；想當年的聖誕前夕發生了香港保衞戰，歷時18日，結果港督楊慕琦於12月25日簽署降書，開始了「三年零八個月」的日據時期。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然戰敗了，但深入了解的話，面對人數多過己方一倍，並有制空權與強大炮火支援的日軍，香港守軍已經克盡己職，其英勇表現理應值得肯定、懷緬，只可惜香港人太善忘了，讓這重要一章，變成被遺忘的歷史。還幸，從外國的Living Monument得到啟發，兩位90後的香港歷史有心人&mdash;&mdash;Taurus和Kevin，聯同一班志同道合者，剛剛舉行了本地首次的香港保衞戰Living Monument紀念活動，Watershed Hong Kong的召集人Taurus解說︰「以前的香港男士有義務去當兵，深入認識的話，自會發現守軍的來源相當多元化，有英國人、加拿大人、印巴裔、歐亞混血兒與本地華人，一齊為香港作戰，當時守軍保家衞國的精神，很值得我們尊敬與回顧。特別的是有些港大的校友，當時在黃泥涌作戰，家園就在大坑，他們在機槍堡中可以望到家園。時代不同，但在同一片土地上，以前有一班年輕人面臨生死抉擇。」當兵，不但責任重大，而且生死攸關，絕用以解決年輕人住屋需求的取巧之策，口出此言賺Sound Bite的政客，可有認清當年歷史？對保衞戰中犧牲的軍人，可會感到愧疚？"},{"pid":"aa1a515be0355063a45c1a95fbae37ba1f402ba8","tid":41754,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"回顧這段歷史，有評論云守軍表現不似預期，甚至認為英國當局放棄香港防務，Kevin持反調︰「當時日軍與守軍的兵力相當懸殊，相比其他遠東戰役，香港守軍堅持了18日，已經是比較長的日數，而且的確表現奮勇。」曾為是次活動主持講座的浸會大學歷史系助理教授鄺智文亦言︰「除了建築醉酒灣防線，開戰前不久還有兩營加軍來港協防。其實在1941年中，英國、美國、澳洲、紐西蘭與加拿大等國都有共識，尤其是以英國牽頭，一齊派兵到亞洲，期望利用威攝戰略，讓日本打消或延遲在亞洲開戰，香港可從中爭取時間加強防務，可惜事與願違；其實這兩營加軍只是先頭部隊，尚有加拿大援兵準備來港，無奈已來不及了，如此情況也在亞洲其他戰場發生。另一方面，與同時期的馬來亞與爪哇戰事的英軍相比，香港守軍的表現已相當不俗了，而且根據進攻香港的日軍內部報告可知，日軍承認己方表現欠佳，反之守軍抵抗很強烈。」 <br />\n<br />\n到底誰是誰非？本地歷史關注團體Watershed Hong Kong，便希望藉今次活動引起市民興趣，從而深入了解香港保衞戰的來龍去脈。早於今年九月開始，有關方面在社交網站公開招幕演員與導賞員，其後舉行了研習講座、步操訓練與綵排，做足準備之後，首日活動已本月11日在尖沙咀碼頭舉行，到底實際情況如何？市民有何反應？箇中種種在「Part 2」再續。 <br />\n<br />\nFacebook︰Watershed Hong Kong"},{"pid":"fb78638a787ce7fc2aa0cde57989030fc2f793ab","tid":41754,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_02b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_02b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=e5508255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次的「守軍」就與當年一樣，既有本地華人，亦有居港洋人，能夠聚首一堂，緣於對香港歷史的尊重。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_03b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_03b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=6475e772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是次活動的演員，全數劃一穿上當年的Khaki Drill守軍制服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_04b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_04b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=556dd005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首日活動於尖沙咀碼頭舉行，「守軍」於碼頭至鐘樓一帶巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_05b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_05b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=d448b522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在尖沙咀逗留約兩個半小時後，「守軍」乘坐小輪移師中環。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_06b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_06b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=8c561c0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主辦單位期望藉Living Monument的模式，帶來比傳統講座或展覽更大的吸引力，從而引起市民興趣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_07b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_07b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=0d73792d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTaurus（右）與Kevin（左）認為香港保&amp;#34910;戰是本地史的重要一頁，但普遍市民對之認識甚少，故此效法外國的Living Monument，希望喚起市民關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_08b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_08b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=ee6672e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n活動正式舉行前，主辦當局舉辦了研習講座，邀請了香港浸會大學歷史系助理教授鄺智文深入講述香港保&amp;#34910;戰的前因後果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_09b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_09b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=6f4317c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「守軍」的步操教官一職，由前華籍英軍黃禮明先生擔任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_10b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_10b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=99e0de54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為應對日軍威脅，<em>港英當局</em>在戰前已加緊構築戰防工事，包括圖中的摩星嶺炮台。"},{"pid":"e132ed9fe540542c36dd0f2c9b7a3f9c500413aa","tid":41754,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_11b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_11b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=18c5bb73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於柴灣的西灣國殤紀念墳場，是香港保&amp;#34910;戰殉職守軍的其中一個主要墓園。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_12b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_12b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=40db125b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來港協防的兩營加拿大援軍，分別是皇家加拿大來福槍營（上）與溫尼柏榴彈兵營（下）。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_13b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_13b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=c1fe777c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨加軍到港的根達中士，為了拯救受傷的守軍，最後叼走日軍的手榴彈遠走，爆炸身亡。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_14b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_14b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=f0e6400b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n守軍方面，除有四營英軍與兩營加軍，還有一連香港華人軍團。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_15b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_15b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=71c3252c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1941年12月12日早上，日軍抵達天星碼頭並與英軍印度旁遮普營與蘇格蘭營交戰，守軍最後成功上船撤退至港島。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/photo/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_16b.jpg?20161215215559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001_16b.jpg%3F20161215215559&h=29dd8c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港督楊慕琦於12月25日到半島酒店簽署降書，赤柱守軍於翌日投降，歷時18日的香港保&amp;#34910;戰正式結束。（互聯網圖片"},{"pid":"b150b24daed2e96099ec2d4529e146bfd97c7543","tid":41754,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161216%2Fbkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001.html&d=BHVGhwENv8XoGng4fVoh0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=3842d86c\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161216/bkntw-20161216111102280-1216_04511_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"706459bb62b137b92fc6e82e54702b12015055c4","tid":41754,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:42:00.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.theatlantic.com/assets/media/img/mt/2016/07/RTX2J8X1/lead_960.jpg?1467408040\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.theatlantic.com%2Fassets%2Fmedia%2Fimg%2Fmt%2F2016%2F07%2FRTX2J8X1%2Flead_960.jpg%3F1467408040&h=1fde7d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">A Living War Memorial Stands Silent Guard Across the U.K.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nMore than a thousand volunteer actors gave tribute to the fallen soldiers of the Somme<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2016/07/somme-centennial-memorial/489866/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Finternational%2Farchive%2F2016%2F07%2Fsomme-centennial-memorial%2F489866%2F&d=BHVGhwENv8XoGng4fVoh0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=416b56b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2016/07/somme-centennial-memorial/489866/</a>"},{"pid":"6fd2f7a7c70e8111a273acdd56820bf55538af77","tid":41754,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7757e39dd9ea312fa80412bbc0b6a0174328a43","tid":41754,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:14:19.000Z","msg":"英軍當年死得幾慘有眼睇，唔通要英國調隊主力黎守你個殖民地咩<br />\n<br />\n成鳩日叫我地學歷史愛國（共）<br />\n唔知當年偉大既共產黨又點樣保衛過香港，值得我地愛佢呢？"},{"pid":"23ee58e756e4b3da0202948e1a7f1e6b9e99b2d6","tid":41754,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"其實樓主想回應番日治香港d相果個post<br />\n提醒番d人"},{"pid":"770031298783bc03fb463f62f857dfc560ca1bed","tid":41754,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:19:56.000Z","msg":"請大家由得呢個5毛帖沉，唔好再推，thanks！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e3e6f8080c1ff12219e3131f558e498e8b2a8f","tid":41754,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實樓主想回應番日治香港d相果個post<br />\n提醒番d人</blockquote><br />\n啱啱今日新聞出先貼咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514b88a509be9ee8c0de7ccec207fce22db6af79","tid":41754,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英軍當年死得幾慘有眼睇，唔通要英國調隊主力黎守你個殖民地咩<br />\n<br />\n成鳩日叫我地學歷史愛國（共）<br />\n唔知當年偉大既共產黨又點樣保衛過香港，值得我地愛佢呢？</blockquote><br />\n當年英國艦隊喺地中海同意大利、北海同德國擊戰緊，遠東艦隊又要守新加坡，可以調派嘅兵力真係唔多。<br />\n<br />\n所以兩個加拿大營來左香港，莫德庇重想叫加拿大送多一營來，湊夠一個加拿大旅；喺新加坡嘅遠東總司令重積極向倫敦爭取調派多啲戰機來香港，重威脅話如果香港因為失去制空權而來英聯邦部隊遭受無辜犧牲，倫敦要付上所有政治責任。兩樣都係因為戰爭提早爆發先唔成事。"},{"pid":"67a45cf663d8a4b50d90cf7e39fc5f8a6a61069c","tid":41754,"uid":5751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:38: